Manufacturer relationship messaging
C/S and Altro should be highlighted because they have been instrumental in the company’s growth.
However, the site should frame the business as a contractor that understands many systems and selects the
right product for the application, specification, and budget — not as a salesperson for a single brand.
• Use language like: ‘We regularly work with products from leading manufacturers including Construction
Specialties, Altro, Inpro, Panolam, Marlite, and others.’
• Use an About-page note such as: ‘Over the years we have developed particularly strong relationships
with manufacturers such as Construction Specialties and Altro, whose products are widely used in
healthcare and institutional environments.’
• Avoid language such as ‘best product’, ‘superior to competing brands’, or direct product put-downs.

